Well, that tenon came out
a lot smaller than it was

00:04:05.345 --> 00:04:07.980
supposed to. And I was
puzzling over my math,

00:04:07.981 --> 00:04:10.149
where I could have gone
wrong, maybe the templates

00:04:10.150 --> 00:04:12.818
the wrong size. And then
I realized I still had a

00:04:12.819 --> 00:04:15.321
3/4 inch guide
bearing on there.

